                    <p>We encourage experimentation and creativity. Some of our best-selling flavors started as wild ideas in our kitchen lab!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-hands-helping"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Team Collaboration</h4>
                    <p>Great ideas come from collaboration. Our chefs, makers, and servers work together to create the complete Creamy Bar experience.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="500">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    </div>
