                    <p>We're committed to sustainable practices, from sourcing local ingredients to using eco-friendly packaging. Our team is dedicated to reducing our environmental footprint.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="600">
                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-award"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h4>Excellence</h4>
                    <p>We never compromise on quality. Every team member is dedicated to excellence in their role, ensuring our customers receive only the best.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
